SOFT & COMFY FEEL - Our best tri-blend fabric comes together for incredible softness and comfort.
RECYCLED FIBERS - Made from a portion of recycled polyester fibers for a lightweight, soft feel.
FITS JUST RIGHT - Comfy and relaxed, this women's t-shirt is perfect for all things casual.
DESIGN DETAILS - This long sleeve t-shirt for women has a set-in ribbed crewneck and a curved hem with a cover stitching.

feature_bullets: SOFT FABRIC: Our men's classic short sleeve graphic t-shirts are made of 100% cotton; The tees are finished with a screen printed back neck label for constant comfort throughout

REGULAR FIT: Our men's classic graphic tee shirts come in a regular fit, offering slightly more room in the chest, shoulders, and body; A perfect addition to your closet and wardrobe, pair our tees with RVCA shorts, pants, jeans, or boardshorts
TAG-FREE NECK LABEL: Our men's short sleeve graphic tees feature a tagless back neck label for extra comfort without having to deal with a tag
RVCA: Shop our collection of graphic tees, tanks, hats, boardshorts, shorts, hoodies, shirts, flannels, kids wear, jeans, pants, backpacks, and beanies

The RVCA name (pronounced: REW-KA) was developed first and foremost out of the "V" and "A" which symbolizes the balance of opposites and how they coexist: Nature x Industrialization, Women x Man, Past x Present…Future. Today. Tomorrow. Life.
